<v SPEAKER_1>Okay, sounds good.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:49.000
<v SPEAKER_1>Let's, let's skip all the personal stuff and go into Ninepine, because that's probably what people want to hear about, and what I want to hear about.

00:04:49.760 --> 00:05:07.620
