00:06:05.060 --> 00:06:18.760
<v SPEAKER_2>But I think people should just kind of be careful when you listen to podcasts or hear people speak, because I guess with the, quote unquote, like, success, everything is relative.

00:06:18.760 --> 00:06:27.540
