<v SPEAKER_2>What's their training habits?

00:06:53.280 --> 00:07:00.780
<v SPEAKER_2>Just so they can perhaps replicate, you know, their skill or their kind of external success to a certain level.

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:09.960
