00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:22.720
<v SPEAKER_2>Like, I don't feel that I'm really in the whole, like, say, retail ecosystem in Sweden, possibly because I'm already like an immigrant outsider.

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:26.000
