00:07:26.060 --> 00:07:31.400
<v SPEAKER_2>I'm super into, like, like, stoicism, like, just as a grounding.

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:40.040
<v SPEAKER_2>So I guess not let oneself be carried away by the ups and the noise.

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:45.480
<v SPEAKER_2>And at the same time, by not getting carried away with that, you don't get carried away with the lows as well.

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:55.000
<v SPEAKER_2>Because I guess one of the risks of being too, like, personally involved in the ego when it comes to people talking about us, oh, wow, you did this, blah, blah, blah.

00:07:55.540 --> 00:08:05.380
