00:08:05.380 --> 00:08:07.840
<v SPEAKER_2>So kind of hedging my emotional bets.

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:08.700
<v SPEAKER_1>Is that always good?

00:08:08.700 --> 00:08:12.580
<v SPEAKER_1>Isn't it kind of nice to enjoy the ups and downs a bit?

