00:09:34.060 --> 00:09:42.840
<v SPEAKER_2>And the funny thing is that when we started Ninepine, like we had this goal of like hitting this 100 million Swedish krona mark, and like we achieved that.

00:09:42.840 --> 00:09:46.360
<v SPEAKER_2>But the goalposts just keep moving.

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:47.660
<v SPEAKER_2>They're always moving.

00:09:47.660 --> 00:09:53.460
