<v SPEAKER_2>And being able to pay myself a salary was like, back then, that was success.

00:10:23.020 --> 00:10:25.120
<v SPEAKER_2>And I still feel really proud that I can pay myself a salary.

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:30.560
<v SPEAKER_2>And not even that, I mean, you know, it's like now we're supporting other people and other people's families.

00:10:30.620 --> 00:10:32.380
