00:12:01.820 --> 00:12:13.540
<v SPEAKER_2>And with that perspective, it's also like, you know, on a personal level, like, you know, I live in Solna in Stockholm, and like, you know, just a new cafe opens, I mean, or like a new restaurant opens.

