00:13:19.660 --> 00:13:21.480
<v SPEAKER_1>Okay, yeah.

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:38.060
<v SPEAKER_1>If we go back to when you started this company, was there, it's very easy to think in like a retrospect, but was there something actually different with Ninepine compared to the other companies that you guys started?

